universum.studios.android.preference

Interface SharedPreferencesCache


  • public interface SharedPreferencesCache
    Interface that specifies a layer for caches that may be used to store values of SharedPreferences in a memory.
    Author:
    Martin Albedinsky

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static class  SharedPreferencesCache.NotInCacheException
      An exception that may be used by implementations of SharedPreferencesCache to indicate that they have no value stored for a requested key.

    • Method Detail

      • isEmpty

        boolean isEmpty()
        Checks whether this cache is empty or not.
        Returns:
        True if this cache does not have any values stored, false if there is at least one value stored.

      • contains

        boolean contains(@NonNull
                 String key)
        Checks whether there is stored value for the specified key in this cache.
        Parameters:
        key - The key of which value presence to check.
        Returns:
        True if there is value presented for the specified key, false otherwise.

      • putString

        boolean putString(@NonNull
                  String key,
                  @Nullable
                  String value)
        Puts the given string value for the specified key into this cache.

        If there is already stored value for the specified key in this cache it will be replaced by the new one.

        Parameters:
        key - The key for which to put the value into cache.
        value - The desired value to put into cache.
        Returns:
        True if put has been successful, false otherwise.

      • getString

        @Nullable
String getString(@NonNull
                            String key)
        Retrieves the string value for the specified key stored in this cache.
        Parameters:
        key - The key for which to retrieve its associated value.
        Returns:
        The value associated with the key.
        Throws:
        SharedPreferencesCache.NotInCacheException - If there is no value stored in this cache for the requested key.
        See Also:
        contains(String)

      • evict

        boolean evict(@NonNull
              String key)
        Evicts a value for the specified key stored in this cache.
        Parameters:
        key - The key for which to evict its associated value.
        Returns:
        True if value associated with the key has been evicted, false if there was no value stored in this cache for the specified key.

      • evictAll

        int evictAll()
        Evicts all values stored in this cache.
        Returns:
        The number of values that has been evicted. May be 0 if this cache is empty.
